[This in spite of a report of 5 Dec 2014 that there are 3 new hotspots of Ebola in Monrovia; see Ebola virus disease - West Africa (222): S. Leone doctors die, WHO, Guinea, blood 20141207.3017499 item [4]. Politics trumping public health yet again. - Mod.JW]

